<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q27_v6" title="Q27_v6" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float"><qti-default-value><qti-value>0</qti-value></qti-default-value></qti-outcome-declaration><qti-item-body>
    <p>Se sabe que al expresar el trinomio
      <m:math>
        <m:mrow>
          <m:msup>
            <m:mi>x</m:mi>
            <m:mn>2</m:mn>
          </m:msup>
          <m:mo>+</m:mo>
          <m:mn>5</m:mn>
          <m:mi>x</m:mi>
          <m:mo>−</m:mo>
          <m:mn>24</m:mn>
        </m:mrow>
      </m:math>
      como producto de dos binomios de la forma
      <m:math>
        <m:mrow>
          <m:mo>(</m:mo>
          <m:mi>x</m:mi>
          <m:mo>+</m:mo>
          <m:mi>a</m:mi>
          <m:mo>)</m:mo>
          <m:mo>(</m:mo>
          <m:mi>x</m:mi>
          <m:mo>+</m:mo>
          <m:mi>b</m:mi>
          <m:mo>)</m:mo>
        </m:mrow>
      </m:math>,
      los números <em>a</em> y <em>b</em> deben cumplir simultáneamente que su suma es 5 y su producto es −24.
      ¿Cuál de las siguientes parejas ordenadas (a, b) cumple ambas condiciones?
    </p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      <qti-prompt>Elige la opción correcta.</qti-prompt>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo>
            <m:mn>6</m:mn>
            <m:mo>,</m:mo>
            <m:mo>−</m:mo>
            <m:mn>4</m:mn>
            <m:mo>)</m:mo>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Para <em>a</em> = 6 y <em>b</em> = −4, se cumple 6 · (−4) = −24, pero la suma es 6 + (−4) = 2, y no 5. Entonces esta pareja no cumple ambas condiciones simultáneamente.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo>
            <m:mn>8</m:mn>
            <m:mo>,</m:mo>
            <m:mo>−</m:mo>
            <m:mn>3</m:mn>
            <m:mo>)</m:mo>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Para <em>a</em> = 8 y <em>b</em> = −3, la suma es 8 + (−3) = 5 y el producto es 8 · (−3) = −24. Por lo tanto, esta pareja satisface exactamente las dos condiciones del problema.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo>
            <m:mn>9</m:mn>
            <m:mo>,</m:mo>
            <m:mo>−</m:mo>
            <m:mn>4</m:mn>
            <m:mo>)</m:mo>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Para <em>a</em> = 9 y <em>b</em> = −4, la suma es 9 + (−4) = 5, pero el producto es 9 · (−4) = −36, y no −24. Entonces esta pareja no cumple ambas condiciones simultáneamente.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo>
            <m:mn>8</m:mn>
            <m:mo>,</m:mo>
            <m:mn>3</m:mn>
            <m:mo>)</m:mo>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Para <em>a</em> = 8 y <em>b</em> = 3, la suma es 8 + 3 = 11, y además el producto es 8 · 3 = 24. No se cumple ni la suma 5 ni el producto −24.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso por suma y producto</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Relacionar el trinomio con los binomios</strong></p>
            <p>Si
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mo>(</m:mo>
                  <m:mi>x</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mi>a</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>)</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>(</m:mo>
                  <m:mi>x</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mi>b</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>)</m:mo>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
              se desarrolla, resulta
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:msup>
                    <m:mi>x</m:mi>
                    <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                  </m:msup>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>(</m:mo>
                  <m:mi>a</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mi>b</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>)</m:mo>
                  <m:mi>x</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mi>a</m:mi>
                  <m:mi>b</m:mi>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>.
            </p>
            <p>Comparando con
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:msup>
                    <m:mi>x</m:mi>
                    <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                  </m:msup>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>5</m:mn>
                  <m:mi>x</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>24</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>,
              se obtiene que
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mi>a</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mi>b</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>5</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
              y
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mi>a</m:mi>
                  <m:mi>b</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>24</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>.
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Revisar cada alternativa</strong></p>
            <p><em>Opción A:</em>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>6</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>(</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>4</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>)</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
              y
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>6</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>×</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>(</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>4</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>)</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>24</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>.
              Cumple el producto, pero no la suma.</p>
            <p><em>Opción B:</em>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>8</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>(</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>)</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>5</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
              y
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>8</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>×</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>(</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>)</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>24</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>.
              Cumple ambas condiciones.</p>
            <p><em>Opción C:</em>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>9</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>(</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>4</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>)</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>5</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
              y
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>9</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>×</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>(</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>4</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>)</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>36</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>.
              Cumple la suma, pero no el producto.</p>
            <p><em>Opción D:</em>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>8</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>11</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
              y
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>8</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>×</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>24</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>.
              No cumple ninguna de las dos condiciones.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Concluir</strong></p>
            <p>La única pareja ordenada que cumple simultáneamente
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mi>a</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mi>b</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>5</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
              y
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mi>a</m:mi>
                  <m:mi>b</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>24</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
              es
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mo>(</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>8</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>,</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>)</m:mo>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>.
            </p>
            <p>Por lo tanto, la respuesta correcta es la <strong>opción B</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>